('96632','33348','5','Sea View Villa with sep. Guest apartment in Capdepera'),
('96633','33349','5','Capdepera is located on the northeast coast of Mallorca only a few kilometers from Arta and Cala Ratjada away. The villa stands on a ca 870m² of land with very beautiful view of the Cala n''Aldern. The ca 520m² living space is spread over 3 floors. In the main house there is a living-dining room, kitchen, 5 bedrooms 4 bathrooms. About the garden level you reach a separate guest apartment with living-dining room, kitchen, 3 bedrooms and a bathroom. Equipped with wooden double glazed windows, fitted kitchen and underfloor heating (heat pump newer). In very beautiful Mediterranean garden is a pool. This very well maintained house can be taken furnished.'),
